              </div>
              <div style="background: #1F2527; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <code style="color: #A0A0A0;">&lt;span class="sit-badge sit-badge-success"&gt;SUCCESS&lt;/span&gt;</code>
              </div>

