  &lt;div class="sit-progress-bar" style="width: 75%;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
              </div>

              <h4 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Spinners</h4>
              <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div class="sit-spinner sit-spinner-sm"></div>
                <div class="sit-spinner"></div>
                <div class="sit-spinner sit-spinner-lg"></div>
              </div>
              <div style="background: #1F2527; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <code style="color: #A0A0A0;">&lt;div class="sit-spinner sit-spinner-lg"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
              </div>

              <h4 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Cards</h4>
              <div class="sit-card" style="max-width: 350px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div class="sit-card-header">
                  <h4 class="sit-card-title">Card Title</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="sit-card-body">Card content here.</div>
                <div class="sit-card-footer"><span class="sit-text-muted sit-text-sm">Footer</span></div>
              </div>
              <div style="background: #1F2527; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <pre style="margin: 0; color: #A0A0A0;"><code>&lt;div class="sit-card"&gt;
  &lt;div class="sit-card-header"&gt;&lt;h4 class="sit-card-title"&gt;Title&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sit-card-body"&gt;Content&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sit-card-footer"&gt;Footer&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
              </div>

              <h4 style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Tooltips (CSS-only)</h4>
              <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <span class="sit-tooltip">
                  Hover over me
                  <span class="sit-tooltip-content">This is a tooltip!</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div style="background: #1F2527; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto;">
                <pre style="margin: 0; color: #A0A0A0;"><code>&lt;span class="sit-tooltip"&gt;
  Hover over me
  &lt;span class="sit-tooltip-content"&gt;Tooltip text&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;</code></pre>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

</dashboard>
